OL,3,CFootage shows moment stolen forklift
OL,4,Csmashes into family shop
OL,6,FPolice have released footage of the
OL,7,Fmoment ram raiders drove a stolen
OL,8,Fforklift truck through the wall of a
OL,9,Ffamily shop to steal a cash machine.
OL,11,FJohn Charles and Reuben Reynolds used
OL,12,Fthe vehicle to smash their way into
OL,13,Fthe Spar in Wesley Road, Retford, in
OL,14,Fthe early hours of 14 March last year.
OL,16,FThe raid caused #40,000 worth of
OL,17,Fdamage before the pair fled in a white
OL,18,Fvan with false plates.
