OL,6,FBodycam footage from Nottinghamshire
OL,7,FPolice shows officers arresting them
OL,8,Fat a house in Welbeck Road, Retford.
OL,10,FFurther enquires found Charles, 50,
OL,11,Fand Reynolds, 42, had carried out a
OL,12,Fseries of burglaries, including an
OL,13,Fincident where they stole a large
OL,14,Famount of cash from a Retford pub 11
OL,15,Fdays before the ram raid.
OL,17,FThey initially denied the offences but
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty after text messages
OL,19,Fshowed the pair planned the incidents.
