OL,6,FNottingham Crown Court heard they had
OL,7,Fbeen left "disappointed" when they
OL,8,Ffound the cash machine taken from the
OL,9,FSpar was empty.
OL,11,FAt a sentencing hearing today (15
OL,12,FAugust), the court heard the store had
OL,13,Fbeen run by the same family for almost
OL,14,F30 years.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the shop owner said:
OL,17,F"Nothing prepares you for the
OL,18,Femotional feeling of turning up to
OL,19,Fseeing a telehandler and a huge hole
OL,20,Fthrough the side of your store.
