OL,6,F"These awful individuals put at risk
OL,7,F26 years of a family's work. They also
OL,8,Fput at risk an amenity that the local
OL,9,Fcommunity relies on."
OL,11,FAs well as the cost of the damage, the
OL,12,Fcourt heard the shop had lost #28,000
OL,13,Fof business and was facing an extra
OL,14,F#10,000 a year in insurance costs.
OL,16,FCharles, of Welbeck Road, Retford,
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty to attempted burglary,
OL,18,Fburglary, aggravated vehicle taking
OL,19,Fand burglary with intent to steal.
