OL,6,FReynolds, of College Close, Newark,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to the same charges.
OL,9,FBoth men were jailed for four years.
OL,11,FJudge Nirmal Shant KC told the pair:
OL,12,F"I have read the owner's statement
OL,13,Fwith care and it's right to say he's
OL,14,Fbeen utterly affected by what you did
OL,15,Fon that night and will remain affected
OL,16,Ffor many years.
OL,18,F"To describe him as heartbroken is
OL,19,Fputting it mildly."
