OL,6,FPC Liam O'Kane, of Nottinghamshire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "These are appalling
OL,8,Fcrimes and the bearing they've had on
OL,9,Fhardworking and law-abiding victims
OL,10,Fshould not be underestimated.
OL,12,F"The ram raid on the Spar store had a
OL,13,Fparticularly terrible impact on a
OL,14,Ffamily who ` through no fault of their
OL,15,Fown ` have been forced to endure a
OL,16,Fhuge amount of stress and financial
OL,17,Fhardship as a result of this shocking
OL,18,Fburglary."
